author: damien
msg: Deterministic revids, MD5 checking of documents, added tracking of rev when an attachment is edited to allow attachment level replication.

author: fhanik
msg: Async patches phase 1 - Async means the container thread can back out. This means that valves need to be async aware. For example, access log valve, can no longer log upon exit of the method since the thread can back out based on async behavior.
